Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是躲不开你  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no hiding from you, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻点  轻点  没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Easy, easy. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没事  没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're all okay. Yeah, we're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样的  是谁让他们这么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How, how, how did this happen? Who gave them the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是说是我吗  -反正是有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are you suggesting I did? - Someone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人决定了把疏散区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone decided that the evacuation zone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,划为30公里半径  而我们知道  这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}should be 30 kilometers, when we know, here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高美尔区探测到了铯137\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cesium-137 in the Gomel district.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那都是200公里外了  -反正就是决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That's 200 kilometers away! - It was decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-理由呢  -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Based on what? - I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅  或许我是在实验室里待久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forgive me. Maybe I've just spent too much time in my lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是我愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or maybe I'm just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就这么办的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this really the way it all works?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某个共产党官员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An uninformed, arbitrary decision
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业党员做出的无知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that will cost who knows how many lives
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武断的决定  将害死天知道多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}made by some apparatchik, some career party man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是职业党员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a career party man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说话该小心点  列加索夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should watch your tone, Comrade Legasov.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们亲眼证实火几乎被扑灭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have visual confirmation that the fire is nearly extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碘131和铯137的排放量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There has also been a reduction in iodine 131
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有所减少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and cesium-137 emissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是好事  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但温度在上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the temperature is rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锆95排放量激增\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a spike in zirconium-95.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自于燃料棒包覆层上的锆95\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's from the cladding on the fuel rods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明熔毁已经开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The meltdown has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它拿开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get it off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它拿开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get it off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开他  你弄疼他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get off him! You're hurting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不能进来  -他怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You can't be in here. - What's happening to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't be in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\fad(2200,1000)\c&HF3F8F3&\pos(191.2,154.37)}1986年5月2日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}莫斯科请求"帮帮我们"\N熔毁可能在十年内导致一万人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  -谢比纳同志来电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes? - Comrade Shcherbina is on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转接进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put him through.
