Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火快被扑灭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fire's nearly out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起泡箱里的水正被抽出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The bubbler tanks are being drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经成功消除了热爆炸的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have successfully eliminated the risk of a thermal explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但堆芯内部的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The situation inside the core
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熔毁速度比预期更快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is deteriorating faster than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混凝土层能撑六到八周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The concrete pad will last for six to eight weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但之后  列加索夫预测有50%的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but after that, Legasov estimates a 50% chance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料会熔穿混凝土层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the fuel will breach the pad
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流入地下水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and melt down into the groundwater itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些地下水流往哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And where does this groundwater go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普里皮亚季河\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Pripyat River,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终流入第聂伯河\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which feeds into the Dnieper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是约五千万人口的主要供水系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The primary water supply for approximately 50 million people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不用说庄稼和牲畜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not to mention crops and livestock,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此水源将...不能使用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would be... unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们建议在混凝土层下安装热交换器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're recommending we install a heat exchanger under the pad
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以降低堆芯温度  暂停熔毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to lower the core temperature and halt the meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么做  据说我们需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And in order to do that, I'm told that we will need...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全苏联所有的液氮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all of the liquid nitrogen in the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好吧  -当然了  我们还需要...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- All right. - Yeah, and of course, we'll also need--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要什么都给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever you need, you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你现在应该明白了  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That should be clear by now. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还有事吗  -没有了  谢谢您\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Anything else? - No, no, no. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  我想说一下30公里半径的禁区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. I'd like to address the 30-kilometer exclusion zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  什么  列加索夫教授  是你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait, what? Professor Legasov, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么禁区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What exclusion zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是无关紧要的细节  总书记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Minor details, General Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长会议主席雷日科夫已经决定...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um, Premier Ryzhkov has determined that--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他决定了  那就是决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he determined, then he determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  列加索夫教授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, Professor Legasov,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去那里只有一个原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you are there for one reason only.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗  就是制止这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand? To make this stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道什么时候结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to know when this will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是问切尔诺贝利什么时候彻底安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you mean when will Chernobyl be completely safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钚239的半衰期是两万四千年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the half-life of plutonium-239 is 24,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以应该说"这辈子都不会安全"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So perhaps we should just say, "Not within our lifetimes."
