Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会袖手旁观...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not gonna sit back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的小伙子们会发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What will happen to our boys?
