Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜水员  消防员  控制室的操作员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The divers, the firefighters, the men in the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辐射具体会对他们造成什么影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does the radiation do to them precisely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就其中有些人接受的辐照水平而言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the levels some of them were exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电离辐射会破坏细胞结构\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ionizing radiation tears the cellular structure apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮肤会起水泡  变红  然后变黑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The skin blisters, turns red, then black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后会有一段潜伏期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is followed by a latency period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即时效应会缓和下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The immediate effects subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,患者似乎开始恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The patient appears to be recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至显得很健康  但其实不然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Healthy, even. But they aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种现象通常只会持续一两天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This usually only lasts for a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后细胞损伤开始显现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then the cellular damage begins to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨髓坏死  免疫系统失效\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The bone marrow dies, the immune system fails,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,器官和软组织开始分解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the organs and soft tissue begin to decompose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动脉和静脉像筛子般破裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The arteries and veins spill open like sieves,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以至于无法为患者输吗啡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the point where you can't even administer morphine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来止痛  而且会疼到无法想象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the pain, which is... unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天到三周后  必死无疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then three days to three weeks, you are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那些小伙子的结局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is what will happen to those boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And what about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we've...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们受到了持续的照射  但剂量不算大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've gotten a steady dose, but not as much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不足以杀死细胞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not strong enough to kill the cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过持续时间足以造成DNA损伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but consistent enough to damage our DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以早晚...会得癌症\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, in time... cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或再生障碍性贫血  横竖都是死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or aplastic anemia. Either way, fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种角度来说我们还算幸运  瓦列利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In a sense, it would seem we've gotten off easy then, Valery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你知道我为什么要出来走走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now you know why I wanted to take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以肯定我们的工作地点被窃听了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can presume the work site is bugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们的房间  甚至卫生间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And our rooms, even our bathrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一直都在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've been here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们当然一直在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course they've been here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但既然我们能直接看到他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if we're seeing them out in the open now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说明他们想让我们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's because they want us to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've seen that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料的熔化速度超过了预期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fuel is melting faster than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我有个计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know. I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望是热交换器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Heat exchanger, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想问你个问题  同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's something I've wanted to ask you, comrade,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看来你也在思考同一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I see you're already asking yourself the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它怎么会爆炸呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did it explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把数据算了一遍又一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've worked the numbers over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照RBMK反应堆可能的最坏条件来假设\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}presuming the worst possible conditions in an RBMK reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可每次的结论都一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I always get the same answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结论是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不可能爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没办法在这里找到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not going to solve this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在纸上推演没用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有在控制室的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone who was in the control room,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫  阿基莫夫  托普特诺夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dyatlov, Akimov, Toptunov,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都在莫斯科的第六医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they're all in Moscow, Hospital Number 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要查明那晚到底发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to find out exactly what happened that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个时刻  每个决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}moment by moment, decision by decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁他们还活着赶紧去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go now while they're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他们谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为如果我们不弄明白这是怎么发生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because if we don't find out how this happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的事还会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有霍缪克...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, Khomyuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs23\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur8\fad(1800,1200)\c&HF3F8F3&\pos(191.2,159.279)}俄罗斯苏维埃共和国  图拉\N1986年5月3日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听这个  听这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, here's one, here's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西和房子一样大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's as big as a house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每小时要烧20升油\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}burns 20 liters of fuel every hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生很多的黑烟和噪声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}puts out a shit-load of smoke and noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却把苹果切成三块\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and cuts an apple into three pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是本来该把苹果切四块的苏联机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A Soviet machine made to cut apples into four pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这里谁负责  -我是工长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Who's in charge here? - I'm the crew chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是煤炭工业部长谢多夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am Shadov, Minister of Coal Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many men do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一班是45人  一共100人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On this shift, 45 here, a hundred in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要这100人收拾好装备上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need all 100 men to gather their equipment and get in the trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you? To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是国家机密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪射击吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Start shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的子弹不够杀我们所有人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't got enough bullets for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能地杀  而剩下来的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kill as many as you can, whoever's left,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把你们几个都揍得满地找牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they'll beat the living piss out of each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不能这么和我们说话  -闭上臭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You can't talk to us like that! - Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是图拉  这里是我们的煤矿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Tula. This is our mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不知道原因  我们不会走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't leave unless we know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要去切尔诺贝利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're going to Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道那边出什么事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know what's happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们挖煤  不挖尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We dig up coal, not bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应堆燃料即将熔进地下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The reactor fuel is going to sink into the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污染从基辅到黑海的水源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and poison the water from Kiev to the Black Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部水源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且据说是永久性的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forever, they say.
