Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.77,0:49:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意冒犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean no disrespect,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.89,0:49:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知你能否告知我原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I was wondering if you could tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.11,0:49:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证  我根本不知道你指的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I assure you, I don't know who you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.40,0:49:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是被克格勃逮捕的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She was arrested by the KGB.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.36,0:49:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是克格勃第一副主席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are the first deputy chairman of the KGB.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.57,0:49:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.03,0:50:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在逮捕人这种小事  我已经不管了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why I don't have to bother with arresting people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.99,0:50:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你却百忙之中抽空派人监视我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you are bothering with having us followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.75,0:50:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得副主席很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think the deputy chairman is busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.17,0:50:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  这完全可以理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, no. It's perfectly understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.67,0:50:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志  我知道你听说过一些关于我们的传言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade, I know you've heard the stories about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.59,0:50:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连我自己听到后  都觉得很震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I hear them, even I am shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.92,0:50:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们并不像人们谣传的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we are not what people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.30,0:50:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是有人在监视你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, people are following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.80,0:50:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人在监视他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People are following those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.56,0:50:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到他们了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.69,0:50:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在监视我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.81,0:50:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克格勃就是一个追责圈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The KGB is a circle of accountability.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.78,0:50:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.19,0:50:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们在这里所做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know the work we're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.91,0:50:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你真的不信任我们吗  -我当然信任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You really don't trust us? - Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.37,0:50:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你应该也听过一句俄罗斯谚语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you know the old Russian proverb:
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.04,0:50:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"没有无条件的信任"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Trust but verify."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.12,0:50:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国人都以为这是罗纳德·里根的名言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the Americans think that Ronald Reagan thought that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.67,0:50:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想象吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.13,0:50:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴与你交谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was very nice speaking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.80,0:50:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.80,0:51:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你愿意为她做担保吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So you will be accountable for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.94,0:51:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.44,0:51:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她叫...  -我知道她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Her name is--  - I know who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.52,0:51:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  教授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good day, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.99,0:51:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这结果出人意料得好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, that went surprisingly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.87,0:51:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表现得像个天真的白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You came off like a naive idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.25,0:51:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真的白痴不是威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And naive idiots are not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.69,0:51:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等文件手续处理完了  我再过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll come back when the paperwork is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.90,0:52:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你没事吧  -他们没有伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are you all right? - They didn't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.58,0:52:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们竟然让个孕妇进屋接触...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They let a pregnant woman into a room with a...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.16,0:52:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.46,0:52:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很愚蠢  我也很愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were stupid. I was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.54,0:52:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫不肯跟我谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dyatlov won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.71,0:52:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫和托普特诺夫都跟我谈了  但...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akimov, yes, Toptunov, yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.18,0:52:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦列利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Valery,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.05,0:52:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akimov...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.68,0:52:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的整张脸都被没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his face was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.14,0:52:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想停止调查吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.77,0:52:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有这个选择吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that a choice I even have?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.28,0:52:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得燃料真的会熔穿混凝土层吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you think the fuel will actually melt through the concrete pad?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.08,0:52:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  有40%的可能吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know. A 40% chance maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.88,0:52:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说是50%\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.96,0:53:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  这些数字都只有一个含义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Either way, the numbers mean the same thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.05,0:53:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"也许"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.18,0:53:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许堆芯会熔穿混凝土进入地下水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe the core will melt through to the groundwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.68,0:53:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我派去挖往反应堆地下的矿工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe the miners who I've told to dig under the reactor
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.02,0:53:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救上百万人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will save millions of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.69,0:53:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我只是让他们白白送死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe I'm killing them for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.03,0:53:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再这样下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want to do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.53,0:53:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想停下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.70,0:53:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.49,0:53:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你也别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think you have a choice any more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.96,0:53:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得哪怕面对愚昧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think, despite the stupidity,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.38,0:53:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谎言  甚至被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the lies, even this...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.17,0:53:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也无法不继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you are compelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.38,0:53:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题已经出现了  你如果找不到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The problem has been assigned, and you will stop at nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.72,0:53:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会罢休\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until you find an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.34,0:53:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你就是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because that is who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.31,0:53:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说我是疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lunatic, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.02,0:53:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一名科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.33,0:54:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他们当时在做安全测试吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know that they were running a safety test?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.42,0:54:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-知道  -不止如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yeah. - There's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.51,0:54:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫说他们当时关闭了反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Akimov says they shut the reactor down,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.72,0:54:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托普特诺夫也确认了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Toptunov confirms it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.35,0:54:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们按下了AZ-5  -显然还不够快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- They pressed AZ-5. - Apparently not soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.14,0:54:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.77,0:54:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说阿基莫夫按下了AZ-5\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They say Akimov pressed AZ-5,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.48,0:54:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后反应堆才爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then the reactor exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.74,0:54:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只有一人这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it had been just one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.86,0:54:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会觉得可能是记错了  甚至是脑子不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would have put it under faulty memory or delusion even,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.87,0:54:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们俩都坚定地表示就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but they both agreed. They were adamant.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.08,0:55:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.84,0:55:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你觉得可能吗  -我觉得这说不通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you think it's possible? - I think it makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.59,0:55:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得如果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think it's what I would say
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.51,0:55:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想掩盖我的错误我就会这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I was trying to cover my own mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.55,0:55:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.72,0:55:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.60,0:55:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就该查下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you should pursue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.73,0:55:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何可能性都要追查下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to pursue every possibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.19,0:55:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管这可能性有多小\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no matter how unlikely,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.94,0:55:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到底是谁或者是什么的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no matter what or who's to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.45,0:55:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回医院再问问阿基莫夫和托普特诺夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll go back to the hospital and reinterview Akimov and Toptunov.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.29,0:55:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们还醒着的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they're still awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.12,0:55:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.46,0:55:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍缪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Khomyuk.

